                    <h3>About</h3>
                    <p></p>
                        <p>This is the combination of a opensource components packaged together and deployed with the minimum of python, html, javascript and css necessary for the app to function.</p>
                        <p>The app itself provides no actual functionality other than a framework with which to securely deploy addons.</p>
                         <p></p>
                         <p>See the <a href="/faq">frequently asked questions</a> page for more information on the app.
                         <hr>
                    <h4>Supported Browsers</h4>
                    <p>This app supports the following web browsers and versions:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Firefox 3.5+</li>
                        <li>Google Chrome 5.0+</li>
                        <li>Safari 4.0+ (except windows)</li>
                        <li>Opera 11.10+ (partial support)</li>
                        <li>Internet Explorer 10+</li>
                    </ul>
